Welcome
Monarch Casino & Resort is dedicated to deliver the ultimate guest experience by providing exceptional services as well as the latest gaming, dining and hospitality amenities.  With a main focus on our guests' superior expectations, we continue to aggressively reinvest in our properties. As a market leader, we invite you to become more familiar with our company, our operations and our management team.
