Monarch Casino & Resort Inc Overview



Website:

N/A

Locations:


                                                             Reno, NV 

                                                

Employees:
1,760




Founded:
N/A
CEO:
John Farahi
Industry:

Coin-Operated Amusement Devices
& 1 other industry



Revenue:
$148,180,230





                                            A coin-operated amusement devices company, Monarch Casino & Resort Inc is situated directly at Reno, NV. It pulls in a yearly revenue of $148.2 million and employs 1,760 people. For its niche allure, Monarch Casino & Resort Inc is receiving quite the notice. The firm is currently headed by CEO John Farahi.
                                        









